  "texts": [
    "Standardizing data file formats and maintaining commonality for effective data management is a pressing issue.• Ensuring reusability and flexibility in the context of unifying CD and KT.",
    "Since both CD and KT are methods for student cognitive modeling, there are commonalities and differences in their approaches.",
    "Therefore, ensuring reusability for commonalities and ensuring flexibility for differences is a major challenge.",
    "• Compatibility for future task scenarios.",
    "In both CD and KT, there are various task scenarios, such as fairness, cold start, and so on."
  ]
}